{"tid":1819261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(英國戰線) 英國脫歐後立法制裁違反人權人士","createTime":"2020-01-10T15:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T07:33:23.000Z","uid":254383,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6745e20603eb84942b51c76258a2d141a44aed49","tid":1819261,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"節錄重點<br />\n<br />\n英國喺一月三十一日脫歐後，會喺二月或者三月立法so called Magnitsky Act 制裁違反人權人士<br />\n<br />\n首階段目標俄羅斯、北韓 同 利比亞，2018 沙特殺美國記者事件亦喺名單之中，制裁措施會包括凍結在英資產<br />\n<br />\n英國會致力聯同盟友 - 加拿大 和 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國</span></strong> 打擊違反人權國家，亦透露歐盟早於上個月已經著手開始草擬歐洲版 Magnitsky Act<br />\n<br />\nSources <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.ft.com/content/38cd4b7e-32fd-11ea-a329-0bcf87a328f2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F38cd4b7e-32fd-11ea-a329-0bcf87a328f2&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=5df75686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.ft.com/content/38cd4b7e-32fd-11ea-a329-0bcf87a328f2</a>"},{"pid":"65571814ecb9bb76d5fe0042d6240c214bde63c6","tid":1819261,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:54:39.000Z","msg":"無支那. 屌"},{"pid":"cc55138f37be8118e44fd4305a40cec7a2cd8b0a","tid":1819261,"uid":46748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:54:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa303ac7b8d60734ba90a4b266ff070ec0a164ed","tid":1819261,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"無香港"},{"pid":"8b4dcd35f5345ba6716a46fac9e80c79d4652ca8","tid":1819261,"uid":79916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"bfbfed678cbac53b5ef7c72584df20f74c0c5d87","tid":1819261,"uid":296369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:58:56.000Z","msg":"香港國際團隊要開始準備進一步lobby 